text: The Satav Koli, or Sataw Koli is a clan of Malhar Koli caste found in the Indian state of Maharashtra. The Satav clan of Kolis was hereditary priest and responsible for Mahalaxmi temple of Dahanu and considered the Mahalakshmi as their clan deity. Satav Kolis also served as the royal priest to the rulers of Jawhar State. == See also == * Mukne dynasty == References == Category:Koli clans
title: Satav Koli
